scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 4-128 comprise the entire Schedule to the 2002 ISDA Master Agreement, starting with the heading 'SCHEDULE' and including all the negotiated terms (Parts 1-5) between the parties. The lines before line 4 are cover/exhibit information, and lines after 128 are execution blocks and signatures, not part of the substantive Schedule. No CSA annexes or standard pre-print sections are included in this span.
